{
  "stem": "18670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 353.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew, even though there were times that, you know, you're a young fella.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your mind works and you say to yourself, maybe the Jewish solution would be if all Jews were to convert.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did that-- did that cross your mind?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the age I was 14, 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you hear history, that even though the Jews in Spain converted it didn't make any difference, because 500 years later they're still called [SPANISH] and they're still called-- their Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you realize that even in Vienna, there are many converts that have married Gentiles and mixed marriages.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially after Hitler came, there were kids that were anti-Semitic in school and discovered all of a sudden they had a Jewish ancestor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, to us, it was easy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To them, that was horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It depend how much money you had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mine was on Tisha B'Av, at the [INAUDIBLE] temple in the 20th District.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Temple was full of people, over 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to perform well, because one uncle was the president.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other uncle was on the board.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it would be a [INAUDIBLE], right, if I failed the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then after the bar mitzvah, we had a little party at the-- another uncle, my grandfather's brother, who had raised my mother and her brother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had a cafe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't-- it was in the evening, after sundown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was before Hitler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 1932, my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '38.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- when they marched in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, German troops moved very fast into Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they moved for the borders, to prevent anybody from escaping.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
